### TanStack Query v5 Patterns
```tsx
// Query key factory
export const itemKeys = {
  all: ['items'] as const,
  lists: () => [...itemKeys.all, 'list'] as const,
  list: (filters: Filters) => [...itemKeys.lists(), filters] as const,
  details: () => [...itemKeys.all, 'detail'] as const,
  detail: (id: string) => [...itemKeys.details(), id] as const,
};

// Hook with unified object API (v5)
export function useItems(filters: ItemFilters) {
  return useQuery({
    queryKey: itemKeys.list(filters),
    queryFn: () => api.getItems(filters),
    staleTime: 5 * 60 * 1000,
    placeholderData: keepPreviousData,
  });
}

// Mutation with optimistic update
export function useUpdateItem() {
  const queryClient = useQueryClient();
  return useMutation({
    mutationFn: api.updateItem,
    onMutate: async (updated) => {
      await queryClient.cancelQueries({ queryKey: itemKeys.detail(updated.id) });
      const previous = queryClient.getQueryData(itemKeys.detail(updated.id));
      queryClient.setQueryData(itemKeys.detail(updated.id), updated);
      return { previous };
    },
    onError: (err, _vars, context) => {
      queryClient.setQueryData(itemKeys.detail(context?.previous?.id), context?.previous);
      // Kullaniciya hata mesaji goster (getErrorMessage ile response.data.message/errors)
    },
    onSettled: () => {
      queryClient.invalidateQueries({ queryKey: itemKeys.lists() });
    },
  });
}
```

### Zustand (Minimal Client State)
```tsx
interface UIStore {
  sidebarCollapsed: boolean;
  toggleSidebar: () => void;
  theme: 'light' | 'dark';
  setTheme: (t: 'light' | 'dark') => void;
}

export const useUIStore = create<UIStore>((set) => ({
  sidebarCollapsed: false,
  toggleSidebar: () => set((s) => ({ sidebarCollapsed: !s.sidebarCollapsed })),
  theme: 'light',
  setTheme: (theme) => set({ theme }),
}));

// Selector ile sadece gerekli slice (re-render onleme)
const collapsed = useUIStore((s) => s.sidebarCollapsed);
```

## Form Pattern (react-hook-form + Zod)
```tsx
const schema = z.object({
  name: z.string().min(1, 'required').max(200),
  email: z.string().email('invalid_email'),
  quantity: z.number().int().positive(),
});
type FormData = z.infer<typeof schema>;

function ItemForm({ onSubmit }: { onSubmit: (data: FormData) => void }) {
  const { control, handleSubmit, formState: { errors } } = useForm<FormData>({
    resolver: zodResolver(schema),
  });
  return (
    <Form layout="vertical" onFinish={handleSubmit(onSubmit)}>
      <FormItem label={t('name')} error={errors.name?.message}>
        <Controller name="name" control={control} render={({ field }) => <Input {...field} />} />
      </FormItem>
    </Form>
  );
}
```
- **Backend'de mutual exclusion varsa:** API'nin kabul etmedigi birlestirmeyi (ornegin "ya A ya B") formda da engelle: bir Switch/Checkbox acildiginda digerini `form.setValue('otherField', false)` ile kapat (500/400 hata yerine kullanici hata gormesin).

### Yeni endpoint kullanirken (kontrat checklist)
- Request body ile backend komut/validator **zorunlu alanlarini birebir karsilastir**; API tipinde ve formda tum zorunlu alanlar olsun.
- **Mutation'da** `onError` zorunlu: API 400/500 dondugunde kullaniciya hata mesaji goster (response.data.message veya errors); sadece onError ile rollback yeterli degil, mesaj gosterilmeli.
- Kullanilan her degisken (ornegin dropdown options) tanimli olmali; "is not defined" runtime hatasi onlenmeli.

## Rendering Optimization
```
Karar Agaci:
├── Component sik re-render mi? -> React.memo
├── Hesaplama agir mi? -> useMemo
├── Callback child'a prop mu? -> useCallback
├── Liste 100+ item mi? -> react-window (virtualization)
├── Route-level buyuk mu? -> React.lazy + Suspense
├── Initial bundle buyuk mu? -> Dynamic import
```

## Error Handling
```tsx
class ErrorBoundary extends Component<Props, { error: Error | null }> {
  static getDerivedStateFromError(error: Error) { return { error }; }
  componentDidCatch(error: Error, info: ErrorInfo) { logError(error, info); }
  render() {
    if (this.state.error) return <ErrorFallback error={this.state.error} onRetry={() => this.setState({ error: null })} />;
    return this.props.children;
  }
}
```

## i18n (react-i18next)
- ASLA hardcoded string — her zaman `t('key')`
- Namespace: feature bazli (`items.title`, `auth.login`)
- Lazy loading: namespace bazli bundle split
- Pluralization: `t('items.count', { count: 5 })`
- Tarih/sayi: `Intl.DateTimeFormat`, `Intl.NumberFormat`

## Accessibility (WCAG 2.1 AA)
- Her interactive element: keyboard navigable
- Her image: alt text
- Form: label + error association
- Color contrast: min 4.5:1
- ARIA: role, aria-label, aria-expanded
- Focus management: modal/drawer acildiginda focus trap

